<section id="opportunityType">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>opportunities</primary>
      <secondary>creating new types for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Opportunity Type</title>
  <para>To create a new Opportunity Type, select the NEW
  button. The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/opportunityType.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Create New Opportunity Type</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>
  <para>When creating a new Opportunity Type, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Name</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a name to define the Opportunity Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a brief description of the Opportunity Type.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
